{"tid":2392758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共官方出版社「禍」揮春賀年　港堪輿學家：貼咗隨時衰一年","createTime":"2021-02-03T04:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T00:03:14.000Z","uid":271829,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"fbde6d125086dc4dbf48f08d354df8e420f8c30a","tid":2392758,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T04:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2zhZsoYod1WGiAfl3kXvkZh-u8A=/filters:quality(100)/d87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net/02-02-2021/t_2ff2681b58a84d5d8394bb308f7975bc_name_R4326BESCJDMXCRDNA7H3QFDBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2zhZsoYod1WGiAfl3kXvkZh-u8A%3D%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fd87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net%2F02-02-2021%2Ft_2ff2681b58a84d5d8394bb308f7975bc_name_R4326BESCJDMXCRDNA7H3QFDBA.jpg&h=d9fecab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n中國人農曆新年喜愛貼「福」字揮春，惟如果貼了一個「禍」字，真是大吉利是。國家文化部轄下的人民文學出版社早前推出定價為169元人民幣（約203港元）的《五福迎春‧人文年禮2021》新年禮盒，豈料禮盒內的5張「福」字揮春，竟暗藏一個「禍」字。出版社收到反映後即時認錯，兼將禮盒下架和安排退款，但事件惹來網民熱議。堪輿學家唐碧霞指，亂貼「禍」字揮春，確會讓戶主整年運勢欠佳。香港書法家楊祐添向《蘋果》表示，事件除反映出版社事前準備欠嚴謹，更批評5張揮春風格不協調，美術眼光都有問題。<br />\n<br />\n定價為169元人民幣的《五福迎春&middot;人文年禮2021》禮盒原在網上有售，禮盒內除了有揮春，還有國畫門神、對聯、利是封、牛年福襪、啤牌等。有網民發現，禮盒內獲已故書法大師啟功家人授權的五張「福」字揮春，當中竟有一張是「禍」字，有網民揶揄：「出版社連福禍都不分，只管賣東西賺錢！」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210203/EYH6A6P6KBFOVNPW6OBL22W4IY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210203%2FEYH6A6P6KBFOVNPW6OBL22W4IY%2F&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrXjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=4b3c0715\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210203%2FEYH6A6P6KBFOVNPW6OBL22W4IY%2F&h=ec416062\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210203/EYH6A6P6KBFOVNPW6OBL22W4IY/</a>"},{"pid":"65e4f6ecaee40b14d9f9a57e575c04387908dd0f","tid":2392758,"uid":281492,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T04:11:28.000Z","m